Company Overview of Sound Shore Management, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Sound Shore Management, Inc. is an employee owned investment manager. The firm provides its services to pension and profit sharing plans, charitable organizations, corporations, high net worth individuals, investment companies, other pooled investment vehicles, state or municipal government entities, foundations, endowments, and Goldman and Natixis wrap programs. It manages separate client-focused equity portfolios. The firm launches and manages equity mutual funds for its clients. It invests in the public equity markets of the United States. The firm primarily invests in value stocks employing a fundamental analysis with a bottom-up stock picking approach. Sound Shore Management, Inc. was f...
Sound Shore Management, Inc. is an employee owned investment manager. The firm provides its services to pension and profit sharing plans, charitable organizations, corporations, high net worth individuals, investment companies, other pooled investment vehicles, state or municipal government entities, foundations, endowments, and Goldman and Natixis wrap programs. It manages separate client-focused equity portfolios. The firm launches and manages equity mutual funds for its clients. It invests in the public equity markets of the United States. The firm primarily invests in value stocks employing a fundamental analysis with a bottom-up stock picking approach. Sound Shore Management, Inc. was founded in 1978 and is based in Greenwich, Connecticut.
