Customer Service
Customer ServiceWe have established a dedicated and professionally trained staff of customer service representatives to provide the highest level of service to our shareholders. All members of our customer service staff undergo a lengthy and thorough training process which enables the support center to handle both simple and complex requests. We pride ourselves in answering client calls personally from 8 a.m. to 6 p.m. EST, Monday-Friday, so you will not be required to navigate a cumbersome voice response unit. Our goal at the Sound Shore Fund is to provide complete customer satisfaction through a high quality staff and services. 
Contact Us
                        To ensure the security of your account, financial transactions and account inquiries cannot be handled by e-mail. Therefore, please do not include account-specific or personal information (such as Social Security number, account number, or account balance) in your e-mail correspondence. Please write or call us toll-free at 1-(800) 551-1980 if you have any questions. We look forward to hearing from you.
                    
