    and a top 10 holdings concentration of 33.29%. Sound Shore Management's largest holding is Oracle Corp with shares held of 4,753,568.  Sound Shore Management has met the qualifications for inclusion in our WhaleScore system.    WhaleWisdom has at least 65 13F filings in our database for Sound Shore Management. 
                                           






